{"tid":1474771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港流通貨幣總數為5100億港元","createTime":"2019-08-15T09:41:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T12:00:32.000Z","uid":194298,"like":560,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"824237c995b6a73301e7282d350a2bd3c0aae985","tid":1474771,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:41:29.000Z","msg":"鑒於聽日好似大家都好擔心銀行D錢會唔會拎唔返出黎<br />\n我就做左小小研究，分析比大家睇睇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6QYnMKr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6QYnMKr.jpg&h=a8300faa&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/hkstat/sub/sp110_tc.jsp?tableID=120&amp;ID=0&amp;productType=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.censtatd.gov.hk%2Fhkstat%2Fsub%2Fsp110_tc.jsp%3FtableID%3D120%26ID%3D0%26productType%3D8&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdlSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=384cf6c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/hkstat/sub/sp110_tc.jsp?tableID=120&amp;ID=0&amp;productType=8</a><br />\n根據政府統計處資料<br />\n<br />\n截至2019年香港法定流通港幣有5100億，注意係&quot;港幣&quot;<br />\n當中係市民持有既已經有4800億..<br />\n由法定認可機構即係銀行等等既有有大概260億現錢，金管局有40億<br />\n所以如果聽日有個大富豪要去銀行拎多過300億現錢出黎的話，<br />\n銀行就會比唔到佢，叫佢返屋企等下，等到新錢印到出黎先可以比到錢佢<br />\n<br />\n印錢要幾耐無人知，可快可慢<br />\n但銀行日日都有人去提款，唔快D印到出黎比錢人就會好恐慌架喇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以大富豪聽日千奇唔好一次過拎多過300億現金出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我仲要禁錢比家用老母架...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"435b4d0cd7f27d9868f884ea566ab560efae6601","tid":1474771,"uid":194298,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:41:51.000Z","msg":"仆街開錯時事台，財經分析黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca07347f6d92f81c59bb0fb2b5c0ac707ea2930e","tid":1474771,"uid":36775,"like":209,"dislike":5,"score":204,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:43:09.000Z","msg":"多過300億身家都係建制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/so